com.endava.imdb.search.domain.jackson.tvrage

Class ShowInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.endava.imdb.search.domain.jackson.tvrage.ShowInfo

  • public class ShowInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Bianca on 5/24/2014. This class is used in order to map the callback server detailed response to an object. Since the server gives a complex response, the ShowInfo object makes use of other objects in order to map all the corresponding attributes accordingly.
